room_title: Escape room "Bomb Squad" by Hochatown Escape Games in Broken Bow
room_address: 125 North Lukfata Trail Road, Broken Bow, OK 74728
room_description: You work for the ATF. A briefcase bomb has been left behind by a paranoid individual who believes the world is after him and his secrets. You must find the clues and work the puzzles he left behind to defuse the bomb within 60 minutes. If you can not achieve this mission you will be blown away.
